This package contains programs that show Singleton Pattern.

More here : http://java.dzone.com/articles/singleton-design-pattern-%E2%80%93

me.sinu.pattern.singleton.p1 - Simple Singleton without thread synchronization
me.sinu.pattern.singleton.p2 - Shows the problem with the Simple Singleton (in p1) in multithreaded environment.
me.sinu.pattern.singleton.p3 - Thread safe Singleton 